        "answer_count": 3,
        "title": "Problem with double value with Expansion in java , I was trying to add two double values but not giving accuracy",
        "body": "<p>The given values are <\/p>\n\n<p><strong>double double1 = 1.0814449990040142E7; \ndouble double2 = 7.0164302885665664E17;<\/strong><\/p>\n\n<p>result is double1  + double2 = <strong>7.016430288674711E17<\/strong>  in Java <\/p>\n\n<p>Manually calculated value is <strong>701643028867471089<\/strong><\/p>\n\n<p>Can anyone resolve my issue.<\/p>\n",
        "question_id": 52941680,
